external_knowledge:
- "most valuable active contract" refers to the contract with the highest value within its department; 
- "pending or has completed renewal" refers to contracts with a renewal status of 'pending' or 'completed'; 
- "has undergone amendments" refers to contracts with at least one non-null amendment reason.

- Active contracts refer to contracts that are currently in effect or have not yet expired; 
- Audit history includes all changes, updates, or modifications made to the contract details; 
- The ranking of contracts by start date in descending order implies the most recently started contracts are shown first.
